  <brief_title>IGIV Study for Chronic ITP Patients Ages 3-70</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multi-center, Prospective, Open-label, Clinical Trial to Assess the Safety and the Efficacy of a New Intravenous Immune Globulin (IGIV3I Grifols 10%) in Patients With Idiopathic (Immune) Thrombocytopenic Purpura</official_title>
  <sponsors>
